{
  "_comment": "Categories for the secrets agent. Patterns use * as a wildcard (case-insensitive). When the agent is asked for a key, it determines which category the key belongs to. New categories require a fresh master-password popup. Edit this file to recategorize without re-encrypting your secrets.",
  "_comment_2": "bulk_categories is the set of categories the bot loads on startup (one popup loads all of them). Anything outside bulk_categories requires its own popup when first accessed.",

